<p rend="chapter">5. Visamavuttiniddesa-pañcamapariccheda</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="118"><hi rend="paranum">118</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Na’ṭṭhakkharesu pādesu, snā’dimhā yo’ṇṇavā <hi rend="bold">vattaṃ.</hi></p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="119"><hi rend="paranum">119</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Samesu sindhuto jena, <hi rend="bold">pathyāvattaṃ</hi> pakittitaṃ.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="120"><hi rend="paranum">120</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Ojesu jena sindhuto, ta’meva <hi rend="bold">vīparītā’di.</hi></p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="121"><hi rend="paranum">121</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Na,kāro ce jaladhito, <hi rend="bold">capalāvatta’</hi>micce’taṃ.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="122"><hi rend="paranum">122</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Same lo sattamo yassā, <hi rend="bold">vipulā</hi> piṅgalassa sā.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="123"><hi rend="paranum">123</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi><hi rend="bold">Setava</hi>ssā’khilesupi.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="124"><hi rend="paranum">124</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Bhena’ṇṇavā <hi rend="bold">bha’bbipulā.</hi></p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="125"><hi rend="paranum">125</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Eva’<hi rend="bold">maññā ro</hi> catutthā.</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="126"><hi rend="paranum">126</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> No’ṇṇavā ce <hi rend="bold">navipulā.</hi></p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="127"><hi rend="paranum">127</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> To’ṇṇavā tathā’<hi rend="bold">ññā</hi> siyā.</p>

<p rend="centre">Vatta’ppabhedo.</p>

<p rend="hangnum" n="128"><hi rend="paranum">128</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi></p>

<p rend="gatha1"> Nadissate’ttha yaṃ chandaṃ, payoge dissate yadi;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Visama’kkharapādaṃ taṃ, <hi rend="bold">gāthā</hi> sāmaññanāmato.</p>

<p rend="centre">Iti vuttodaye chandasi visamavutti niddeso nāma</p>

<p rend="centre">Pañcamo paricchedo.</p>
